{"id":"7e750a172885851be8479272a25db268b84e4eae3055631824618298ecd8ed0f","item_id":"30d3e2236b:0","text":"Light Filters 用于操控照明结果。在现实世界中，stencils（遮片）和 gels（色片）通常通过改变镜头中光线的颜色、质量和数量来实现这种效果。RenderMan 的 light filters（灯光滤镜）是以同样方式（甚至更多方式）为场景布光的强大且灵活的手段。"}
{"id":"efa6d30d974d62db727919bf1d03477dfa724551aa9712798a19c931cc8eff2d","item_id":"30d3e2236b:1","text":"在 Solaris 中使用 Light Filters 很简单，并能立即改变你的灯光和照明效果！"}
{"id":"65bf498a3f0b2b18cd8af5102e58aa9925b54d66d276962557524a38cfd20640","item_id":"30d3e2236b:2","text":"要添加 light filter（灯光滤镜），只需添加一个专用 LOP 节点，以创建对应的 USD light filter primitive（灯光滤镜图元）。"}
{"id":"1ce300be499bed2480d7fd2532aae235c1c0c726fd2cff46e471abca6bdf730c","item_id":"30d3e2236b:3","text":"之前的"}
{"id":"c77dd41e265323b8efac624c1db5e4ecb1e7453f06e10275540643ce293ff558","item_id":"30d3e2236b:4","text":"PxrLightFilter"}
{"id":"7b786b4362b44c8f40289231a82ca925d4ef0d886b7200f1023351c3f194bea8","item_id":"30d3e2236b:5","text":"LOP 虽然仍可工作，但已弃用。"}
{"id":"4dfc48ee8763c6d81be9e09c93f40ff1cc626d7b2316b02618a7651f26d608d3","item_id":"30d3e2236b:6","text":"然后使用以下任一方法将其分配给灯光："}
{"id":"e220f66e8651702adc84f8c94b8b9b51e416d688a53bbb9ea41694b809a86cb7","item_id":"30d3e2236b:7","text":"使用 PxrAssign LOP（或 PxrAssignLightFilter 别名）。可以用单个 PxrAssign LOP 将多个 light filters（灯光滤镜）分配给多盏灯。"}
{"id":"dc91f40cca5d3ea90618b0228a54e888ce0b68f99fc78a2f43ddfc00b2d1892d","item_id":"30d3e2236b:8","text":"使用 Light Edit LOP，并填写"}
{"id":"2a3461826c4d17fd952c28f72b03a2e89c2b7cc7b3d0beba215ff278003dc7c6","item_id":"30d3e2236b:9","text":"Light Filters"}
{"id":"7df3500170ade8d3e4f0093176bed1db4fd671ed3a75e502eb0a1a388c90a0a3","item_id":"30d3e2236b:10","text":"参数，该参数位于"}
{"id":"75425410734fa1cec691c4fc7d61bd9a35ef9699988d15bba748458044cf92fe","item_id":"30d3e2236b:11","text":"Base Properties（基础属性）"}
{"id":"7508386a20565f5cbc526eee8b3c9f39edeecd576ee90cb3dbb5ce5ac3fe9566","item_id":"30d3e2236b:12","text":"选项卡"}
{"id":"571efbcd1fef9a1e82b268e8ad9c6f87a02b6e745dc672afd16cedb32e818737","item_id":"30d3e2236b:13","text":"将 Light Edit LOP 放在 light filter LOP 之后，并填写"}
{"id":"2a3461826c4d17fd952c28f72b03a2e89c2b7cc7b3d0beba215ff278003dc7c6","item_id":"30d3e2236b:14","text":"Light Filters"}
{"id":"7df3500170ade8d3e4f0093176bed1db4fd671ed3a75e502eb0a1a388c90a0a3","item_id":"30d3e2236b:15","text":"参数，该参数位于"}
{"id":"75425410734fa1cec691c4fc7d61bd9a35ef9699988d15bba748458044cf92fe","item_id":"30d3e2236b:16","text":"Base Properties（基础属性）"}
{"id":"7508386a20565f5cbc526eee8b3c9f39edeecd576ee90cb3dbb5ce5ac3fe9566","item_id":"30d3e2236b:17","text":"选项卡"}
{"id":"21b2dcdf1bab173927d3149d8f9da375b66e788e7ec25536d44976f78fc22b0a","item_id":"30d3e2236b:18","text":"如果分配正确，在 Scene Graph 中，该 light primitive（灯光图元）上应在 light:filters 属性中列出 light filter primitive（灯光滤镜图元）。"}
{"id":"23338fa3bffb3f6d695aefdde3eceebf4647f83e2d40d6651868d70f4dc1205f","item_id":"30d3e2236b:19","text":"要将 light filter（灯光滤镜）作为灯光的子级（如上面的 Scene Graph 所示），只需设置"}
{"id":"d3e50c389efcae9d24da1bca447be3e2f7d44890f93611fbd70e019af7194c7f","item_id":"30d3e2236b:20","text":"Primitive Path（图元路径）"}
{"id":"41239da3971cd9ad8c269f10993c4ab21a0c04d023ddc3f4674e7419cdc3563c","item_id":"30d3e2236b:21","text":"参数，并在 light filter LOP 上填入正确路径（例如使用 ‘/lights/light1/$OS’，而不是默认的 '/lightFilters/$OS’）。"}
{"id":"d029f87e3d80f8fd9b1be67c7426b4cc1ff47b4a9d0a8461c826a59d8c5eb6cd","item_id":"30d3e2236b:22","text":"Example（示例）"}
